## Mike & Char Duhamel

Golfy Golf Academy is led by the dynamic coaching duo of Mike and Char Duhamel, a husband-and-wife team with decades of combined expertise in professional golf and instruction.

Mike, a PGA/LPGA Tour Performance Coach and Class A Canadian PGA Member, brings over 20 years of experience, blending data-driven swing analysis with a passion for unlocking player potential. Char, an LPGA Tour veteran and former NCAA All-American at UCLA, infuses her coaching with tour-level insights and a focus on mental toughness, honed through years of competitive play.

Together, they offer a unique synergy of technical precision and real-world experience, delivering personalized instruction in putting, short game, and full swing at Old Greenwood in Tahoe and Haggin Oaks in Sacramento. Their mission? To empower every golfer—from beginners to pros—to play with confidence and consistency.

