## Frequently Asked Questions

**What should I bring to my first lesson?**  
Just bring your clubs (or we can provide them) and a willingness to learn. We’ll handle the rest, including all tech and practice materials.

**Can I book lessons at both locations?**  
Yes! We offer flexible scheduling at Old Greenwood (May–October) and Haggin Oaks (year-round). You can mix and match locations.

**Are group lessons available?**  
Absolutely. We offer group clinics for up to 4 players, perfect for friends or families. Contact us for details.

**How soon will I see results?**  
Most students see 3-5 stroke improvements within their first 10 hours of coaching, depending on practice commitment.

**Do you offer junior programs?**  
Yes, we have junior camps and private lessons tailored for young golfers. Reach out to learn about upcoming sessions.

